[Nouns] inclusion, admission, comprehension, reception.
composition (inclusion in a compound) [more].
[Verbs] be included in; come under, fall under, range under; belong to, pertain to; range with; merge in.
include, comprise, comprehend, contain, admit, embrace, receive; inclose (circumscribe) [more]; embody, encircle.
reckon among, enumerate among, number among; refer to; place with, arrange under, arrange with; take into account.
[Adjectives] included, including; inclusive; congener, congenererous; of the same class [more]; encircling.
